data.description: Discover a unique and extraordinary residence in Dunnellon, Florida, that defies the typical Florida home stereotype. This captivating cabin/lodge, nestled in the highly sought-after community, boasts a private boat slip along the Withlacoochee River within an exclusive gated enclave. With 3,592 sq ft of unparalleled luxury, this home is a one-of-a-kind retreat. The property features a 50-year architectural shingle roof, including the garage, installed in 2019, ensuring both durability and style. Inside, enjoy two distinct living rooms—one on the lower level and another upstairs—providing versatile spaces for relaxation and entertainment. The residence is equipped with a whole-home generator system, backed by a warranty and fueled by 500 gallons of propane. A remote-controlled propane fireplace with a separate 60-gallon propane tank adds warmth and ambiance. Your security is a top priority, as the home is equipped with a comprehensive system   covering security, fire alarms, and audio/video surveillance, complete with interior cameras. Additional amenities include a 12 x 24 workshop and a home gymnasium with electricity, A/C, cable, and a maintenance-free metal roof. The kitchen is adorned with new appliances, including a refrigerator, and a new washer and dryer. Stay comfortable year-round with a new A/C air handler installed in 2022, complemented by a new A/C fan and defrost control board installed in 2023. As a bonus, the property comes with a home warranty for added peace of mind and all custom made furniture is included, making this Truly a once in a lifetime TURN KEY opportunity to own a piece of Paradise!
